## **Dashboard Overview**

Build a **Supply Chain On-Time Delivery (OTD) Projections Dashboard** that provides a 6-month forward-looking view of delivery performance. The dashboard consists of two main components:

1. **Monthly OTD Summary Table** — Shows actual and forecasted OTD performance by month
2. **At-Risk Pipeline Table** — Shows orders at risk of delay based on current stage and time remaining

