## **DATA SOURCE REQUIREMENTS**

### Required Source Data Table: `CW_Data` (Current Week Data)
The dashboard pulls from a source data table with the following columns:

| Column | Field Name | Description |
|--------|-----------|-------------|
| B | Supplier | Name of the supplier (e.g., "Indo-MIM", "JJG Aero", "Maini") |
| C | Site | Manufacturing/delivery site location (e.g., "Rockford", "Drakes", "Colorado", "Niles") |
| D | Item # | Product/part number identifier |
| G | Due Date | Expected delivery date |
| I | Stage | Current production/delivery stage (see stage definitions below) |
| J | On-Time/Delay | Status indicator with values: "On time" or "Delay" |
| P | Days Until Due | Calculated field: number of days from current date until due date (positive = future, negative = past) |
